      <title>特朗普关税引发贸易战担忧，日本股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/japan-stocks-fall-as-trump-tariffs-stoke-fears-of-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球贸易战的担忧引发科技公司和汽车制造商等出口商的大规模抛售，日本股市下跌，基准东证指数下跌逾2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/japan-stocks-fall-as-trump-tariffs-stoke-fears-of-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 股价震荡后，台积电股价因假期后回归而备受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/tsmc-shares-in-focus-on-return-from-holiday-after-deepseek-jolt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上周全球人工智能相关股票遭遇抛售之后，台湾半导体制造股份有限公司将于周一恢复交易，该公司将成为市场关注的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/tsmc-shares-in-focus-on-return-from-holiday-after-deepseek-jolt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强抵消避险需求，黄金小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对来自加拿大、墨西哥和中国的进口商品征收关税后，金价小幅走低，在全球准备应对贸易战之际，美元飙升超过了避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对美国最大供应国征收关税，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对包括加拿大和墨西哥原油在内的一系列进口产品征收高额关税，威胁到消费者的成本上涨，油价随之飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普关税导致美元和油价飙升、股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对加拿大、墨西哥和中国出口产品征收关税的威胁后，美元飙升，油价上涨，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣布关税后，加密货币成为避险举措的主要冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/crypto-bears-brunt-of-risk-off-moves-after-trump-unveils-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日晚些时候，加密货币的暴跌给美国一些投机性较强的数字资产带来了沉重压力，这表明在唐纳德·特朗普实施新关税后，投资者将在周一市场开盘时大幅降低风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/crypto-bears-brunt-of-risk-off-moves-after-trump-unveils-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税冲击汽车行业，汽车价格可能上涨 3,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/car-prices-face-3-000-increase-as-trump-tariffs-hit-auto-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税将威胁北美各地汽车制造商的生产，并导致汽车价格创下新高，约 2500 亿美元的贸易将受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/car-prices-face-3-000-increase-as-trump-tariffs-hit-auto-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战爆发，投资者买入美元，准备应对股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/markets-look-to-extend-dollar-s-gains-as-trump-starts-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周来，金融市场一直承受着美国引发贸易战的风险，周一重新开市后，金融市场需要面对现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/markets-look-to-extend-dollar-s-gains-as-trump-starts-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 16:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对中国征收 10% 关税后，习近平考虑采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发动新一轮贸易战后，加拿大和墨西哥领导人迅速作出回应，而中国国家主席习近平则在宣布具体反击措施之前稍事休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港上市的中国股票准备应对特朗普关税的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/hong-kong-listed-chinese-stocks-brace-for-trump-tariffs-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普打响关税战的第一枪后，在香港上市的中国股票在休市三个交易日后于周一恢复交易时将面临新的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/hong-kong-listed-chinese-stocks-brace-for-trump-tariffs-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 07:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
